				"Tame a Bald Eagle with Fish Oil."
				""
				"Bald Eagles are neutral large birds found near mountains with plenty of trees. They fly to lakes to grab salmon out of the water or hunt nearby rabbits. They can be lured in and tamed with Fish Oil. They follow typical follower commands. They can be healed with fish and bred with rotten flesh."
